00:00:22.088 --> 00:00:25.525
doesn't always lead to traffic and trust Trump's ranking.

00:00:25.525 --> 00:00:32.499
In this conversation, we dig into Kevin's latest research on how AI overviews are reshaping user behavior on Google

00:00:32.499 --> 00:00:35.335
and what that means for brands heading into Q4. 

00:00:35.335 --> 00:00:41.608
We unpack why product grids are disappearing, how Reddit and YouTube are suddenly influencing chatbot results

00:00:41.608 --> 00:00:46.146
and why content simplicity and structure are now SEO power plays.

00:00:46.446 --> 00:00:50.850
Plus, Kevin shares what's working and what's not when it comes to LLM optimization

00:00:50.850 --> 00:00:54.788
AI-first content, and evolving SEO KPIs.

00:00:54.788 --> 00:00:59.826
As Kevin puts it, search is not just about clicks anymore. It's about answers and influence

00:00:59.826 --> 00:01:02.495
